\c 4
\s Unoratidzwa Mwari ari pachigaro choushe kudenga
\p
\v 1 Shure kwaizvozvi, ndakatarira ndikaona mukova wakazaruka kudenga; nenzwi rokutanga randakanzwa \add rakaita\add* seraiva rehwamanda richitaura neni; richiti: Kwira pano, ndigokuratidza zvinhu zvinofanira kuitika shure kwaizvozvi.
\v 2 Pakarepo ndakava muMweya; zvino tarira, chigaro choushe chakagadzwa kudenga, no\add mumwe\add* agere pachigaro choushe.
\v 3 Iye wakanga agerepo wakanga akafanana nebwe rejasipisi* neresadhio*; kwakanga kunomurarabungu wakakomberedza chigaro choushe, waitaridzika sebwe remaragdhino.
\v 4 Kwakanga \add kune\add* zvigaro zvoushe zvinamakumi maviri nezvina zvakanga zvakakomberedza chigaro choushe; napazvigaro ndakaona vakuru vanamakumi maviri navana vagere vakapfeka nguwo chena; vakanga vane korona dzendarama pamisoro yavo.
\v 5 Napachigaro chovushe pakabuda mheni, nokutinhira nemanzwi; nemwenje minomwe yakanga ichipfuta pamberi pechigaro choushe, iri Mweya minomwe yaMwari.
\v 6 Pamberi pechigaro choushe pakanga pane gungwa regirazi, rakafanana nekrisitaro*; napakati pechigaro choushe, napakapoteredza chigaro choushe, pakanga pane zvisikwa zvina zvipenyu, zvizere nameso mberi neshure.
\v 7 Uye chisikwa chipenyu chokutanga chakanga chakafanana neshumba, chisikwa chipenyu chechipiri chakanga chakafanana nemhuru, chisikwa chipenyu chechitatu chakanga chinechiso chakaita sechomunhu, nechisikwa chipenyu chechina chakanga chakafanana negondo rinobururuka.
\v 8 Nezvisikwa zvipenyu \add izvi\add* chimwe nechimwe chakanga zvine mapapiro matanhatu akapoteredzwa nemeso kunhivi dzose nomukati; haazorori masikati nousiku, achiti: Mutsvene mutsvene mutsvene, iye Ishe Jehovha wehondo, wamasimba ose, iye wakanga aripo, uripo, nouchazouya.
\v 9 Zvino kana zvisikwa zvipenyu izvi zvachimupa kukudzwa nokubwinya iye unogara pachigaro choushe, iye uri mupenyu nokusingaperi peri.
\v 10 Vakuru vanamakumi maviri navana vowira pasi pamberi paiye ugere pachigaro chovushe vachimushumira iye uri mupenyu nokusingaperi-peri, vachikandira korona dzavo pamberi pechigaro choushe, vachiti:
\v 11 Imwi, makafanira haiwa Ishe, Mwari wedu, kuti muvigirwe kubwinya, nokukudzwa, nesimba, nokuti ndimwi makasika zvinhu zvose, zvakavapo, zvakasikwa nokuda kwenyu.
